WILMA BARROWS; ORGANIST FOR BILLY GRAHAM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Wilma Irene (Billie) Barrows, 69, who filled in for an absent organist at a 
Billy Graham youth rally in Asheville, N.C., in 1945, four years before the 
evangelist became internationally famous and then became part of Graham's first 
musical team. Mrs. Barrows, with baritone George Beverly Shea and her husband, 
Cliff, were the first three members of the Billy Graham Evangelistic Assn., and 
