<HEADLINE>
<P>
LUCKLESS BRITISH GAMBLER RUNS AMOK AT CASINO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A frustrated British gambler went from a losing streak to a wrecking spree and 
caused more than $156,000 worth of damage Sunday when he rammed luxury cars in 
a casino parking lot with his truck. 
</P>
<P>
 The man, who was not identified, went "berserk" at the Castle Casino in this 
northwest resort, and of about 20 rammed cars about half were declared 
write-offs, a police spokesman said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
